From: Hana VanCampen <vancampe@uwyo.edu>
Subject: M. Sarraet (1883)
Regarding the M. Sarraet (1883) report, has anyone considered pseudorabies
as a part of the differential? Cattle exhibit extreme pruritus, frenzied
efforts to relieve the itch and CNS signs. (Actually, I noted that a list of
differential diagnoses was not given).
