As to Bruce Akey comments on the "Stetsonville BSE", while this was clearly
not BSE from Dick Marsh's observations what became TME seems to have started
as a bovine TSE, possibly spontaneous. Neither the latter nor BSE have since
been found in North America. -Mod.MHJ]
